ygData.msgSnippet: Gnomes CAN NOT follow Innurukk. The only god we can follow in the dark worship is Bertoxxulous, God of PEstilence and Disease. He is a cool God..trust me. ...
ygData.messageBody:
Gnomes CAN NOT follow Innurukk. The only god we can follow in the dark
worship is Bertoxxulous, God of PEstilence and Disease. He is a cool
God..trust me.
